metadata.name: Creator 1
metadata.description: You already know Frankie, the ugliest PFP you'll ever lay your eyes on. Now, you can finally meet "The Creator", the mad scientist behind these abominations, who, just like his creations, is comically ugly and can be seen rocking a Halloween costume all year round. As an owner of these NFTs, you can choose to search and match the token numbers of Frankie and his creator to unlock future perks and special rewards within the project.
